Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I can't do it." "It's too frustrating."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.97,0:00:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Break down those hurdles.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.14,0:00:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is nothing I can't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.31,0:00:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who is being manipulated on the field?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.82,0:00:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not frightened yet I get told to go away...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The path to the unseen future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I may not be able to choose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Close your eyes, and shuffle your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.51,0:00:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As promised, yes! you are the winner
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.26,0:01:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Never lose! Shuffle your heart,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}definitely, just like cards
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.73,0:01:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that miracle...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.53,0:01:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright! Yugi's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.16,0:01:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought he'd {\b0}always{\b1} existed within Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.85,0:01:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a split personality the Millennium Puzzle merely brought out...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.65,0:01:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But is that just what I {\b0}wanted{\b1} to believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.26,0:01:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.51,0:01:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you come from inside the Millennium Puzzle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.38,0:02:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Lost Memory of the Pharaoh"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We thank you sincerely for choosing Japan to host your exhibit. Welcome to you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.15,0:02:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.33,0:02:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to meet the Egyptian archaeological expert.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking great care with this Ancient Egyptian exhibit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"No matter what, we should never sing about the eras where successive generations are filled with hostility."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.05,0:02:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me. It's a very old joke often told in Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:54.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sincerely hope this Ancient Egyptian exhibit will be a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.64,0:03:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold up, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.57,0:03:31.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We shall now introduce Ishizu Ishtar-san, who has come all the way from Egypt
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in order to display an Ancient Egyptian exhibit at Domino Museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hello, citizens of Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ishtar-san plans to display some of the greatest pieces of Egyptian history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have come to put the Ancient Egyptian exhibit on public display in Japan's Domino City.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what exactly do you plan to display in the exhibit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.71,0:03:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.85,0:04:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a very special exhibit that will display a mural of the eighteen Egyptian dynasties and the many kings that ruled them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This will be the first time these items have been toured abroad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother, it's amazing! It's the first time this has been shown around the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring. I have no interest what happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.70,0:04:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks kind of interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:21.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This exhibit...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.21,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have an Ishizu Ishtar from the Egyptian government who would like with speak to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ishizu Ishtar?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.32,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We sincerely hope that everyone enjoys the exhibit until the last day of its display.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ask that all of you come visit the exhibition as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Domino Egypt Exhibit"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right here. I'll go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome. It's an honor\N to meet you, Mr. Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am aware of Kaiba Corporation's remarkable strides in the high-tech gaming industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Head, everything is going as instructed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one shall enter this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have a funny way of greeting the president of an official company.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am being doubted from the get-go, I may as well take my leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, but I hope you will understand my reasoning for doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.26,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is merely a military strategy to protect the artifices from certain individuals disputing over them within the Egyptian government.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.21,0:05:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.43,0:05:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you could say you caught my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the Bureau of Egyptian Archeology, were formed back in 1857.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.48,0:06:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say we exist as an organization formed to protect ancient artifices from grave robbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, we are observing excavations such as this around the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.65,0:06:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you are searching for someone to dig up mummies for you, I hate to disappoint...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my only interest lies in building high performance silicon chips for electronic game design technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the {\i1}least bit{\i0} interested in a bunch of rocks from thousands of years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You told me on the phone earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.81,0:06:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wouldn't you be interested in getting some rare cards, Mr. Kaiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My only interest in being here is the rare cards you told me about.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't about to tell me that was some sort of trick to lure me here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let us cut to the chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand you {\i1}do{\i0} hold an interest in Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I were to tell you that the cards you cherish so much holds their origin in Ancient Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.81,0:06:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus J. Crawford...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:55.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The game designer that created the present form of Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:57.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:06:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I told you that he created Duel Monsters after a trip to Egypt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although, this fact is not very well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with me. I think it is about time for a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You risked your life in that fire to put the Millennium Puzzle back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} and Honda-{\i1}kun{\i0} that saved us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:56.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.70,0:07:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's on your mind...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.95,0:08:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.78,0:08:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,YUGI!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am about to show you two palettes in the room up ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palettes originated from the Mortuary Temple of the king that ruled during the eighteenth dynasty of Egypt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This holds the origin of Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What in the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They look exactly like Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.75,0:09:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus created Duel Monsters after seeing this palette.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now explain the details of the past existing of both humans and the "Monsters" we've come to know them as...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ancient Egyptians, like many cultures,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.04,0:09:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thought misfortunes were caused by evil spirits, fear and the suffering that existed within people's hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the Pharaoh and his magicians used spells to trap the spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using stone tablets as a source, the spirits were sealed within them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, over time the evil power began to grow within the sealed tablets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon after, a group of priests began to rebel against the king and his magicians.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They used the evil spirits sealed within the stone tablets,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.19,0:09:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a war broke out as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at this other palette.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.00,0:10:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I wanted\N to show you here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at this\N palette long and carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.14,0:10:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Mr. Pegasus did long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain that, just as he did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will find some form of inspiration from this image.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.43,0:10:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:23.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the image carved above him is the Black Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one standing beside the king...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.64,0:10:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is known as the "White Beast Handler".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the creature carved above him is without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.89,0:10:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The young Pharaoh controls the Magician of Black Magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.46,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And one of his own priests, The White Beast Handler, confronts him using the White Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This palette depicts a Duelist battleground that took place several millenniums ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Millennium Puzzle along with another similar item is depicted in this battle between the king and the priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Legend states that when all seven of these items join together, an unimaginable power will be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That story is still told even today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.31,0:11:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the most important thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.60,0:11:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is the battle between the evil priest and the righteous king.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.67,0:11:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that battle continues on even now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.37,0:11:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...don't believe in this palette!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.50,0:11:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what you are thinking, but this is reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.62,0:11:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please accept the truth with an open heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:11:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.07,0:12:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This place is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call upon the divine sun god Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.92,0:12:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon you to become my servant and protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.54,0:12:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deliver onto this evil priest and his followers divine judgment and punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.53,0:12:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O God, deliver unto them your holy judgment!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.92,0:12:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...is this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.68,0:13:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The vision you are experiencing is a Duel that took place 3,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.10,0:13:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.82,0:13:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.42,0:13:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Why...?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.64,0:13:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no idea myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew you would ask me this one of these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.71,0:13:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I have no intentions of lying to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.17,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know my own name or where I came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no memories of my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who {\b0}am{\b1} I? I have no clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The palette describes the history of the eighteenth dynasty that I have been studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.35,0:13:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The names of the eighteen Pharaohs that ruled during that dynasty are recorded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they are the identities of the kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.31,0:13:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.21,0:14:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one knows anything about this king.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this king was destroyed and all records of him were lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall Summon another servant by the will of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall then polymerize this servant with that of another spirit in order to protect our royal highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Servant of evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:39.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God! Bestow onto them your almighty vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, this is the only king to be completely erased from Egyptian history.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.18,0:14:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A nameless Pharaoh from 3,000 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.29,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't listen to any more of this bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.25,0:15:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough of your nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me show you one last vision.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the name of the divine sun god Ra, we shall dominate this fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.81,0:15:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the spirits of those who reigned supreme and have left this world for the underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.54,0:15:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The {\i1}kings{\i0}! And {\i1}ourselves{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.76,0:15:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"King" is a title that is most fitting to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now pay tributes to God in order to realize this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.89,0:15:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.51,0:15:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice these servants and show your divine form before us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.25,0:15:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.75,0:15:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Servant of divine judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.25,0:15:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.45,0:16:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will now be our true victory!\N O God, grant us your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.18,0:16:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are {\i1}God{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what I believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps fate itself leads the souls
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of the king and priest depicted here to battle in present day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even now, after 3,000 years pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.23,0:16:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing but crazy talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.82,0:16:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me to move to our main subject of the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it you are still interested in the rare cards I mentioned over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if I were to tell you that Pegasus himself has hidden them away?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely at the top of the mural.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three depicted atop the palette, from left to right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.70,0:17:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great War God Obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Osiris the Heaven Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Winged Sun Dragon of Ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Three Illusionary Beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In our present day and age, they have come to be known as "God Cards".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,God Cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus created the three rare cards after viewing this palette.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.51,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You probably have heard rumors of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.15,0:17:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that whoever acquires these three rare cards
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will become a legend among the world of Duels, and be granted the highest ranking Duelist's title...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title "King of Kings".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.28,0:17:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I've heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Cards, as they're called, can be used for either good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.81,0:18:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If used by an evil person, they can supposedly take the lives of both the opponent and the player.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are prohibited cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.50,0:18:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as the ultimate weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.03,0:18:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are cards that scared even Pegasus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.87,0:18:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much so that he himself requested that we, the Bureau of Egyptian Archeology,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seal the cards away in various locations within the Valley of the Kings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, before long they were stolen by a certain individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.06,0:18:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.82,0:18:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.35,0:18:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghouls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.79,0:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare Card Hunters operating in secrecy around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sealing rare cards by stealth or force...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...selling them on the back market for profit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've even heard rumors recently that they have begun making counterfeit bootlegs of the rarest cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, before the worst can occur,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we must get the God Cards back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.71,0:19:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sole purpose for us hosting this Ancient Egyptian exhibit is so we can search for the whereabouts of the cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.00,0:19:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that this palette has the ability to attract Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're making this town into a Duel Monsters battlefield?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see now. They are bound to gather here in flocks to seek out the large gathering of Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.46,0:19:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Blue-Eyes as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.97,0:19:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.82,0:19:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great War God Obelisk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only card out of the three that was not stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to retrieve the other two, I am entrusting you with the Great War God Obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}entrusting{\i0} me with this card?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.62,0:19:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you can trust me that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do if I retrieve the rare cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and refuse to give them back?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been fighting this battle for 3,000 years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.26,0:20:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I certainly plan to go after these Ghouls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there {\i1}is{\i0} one condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.89,0:20:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.56,0:20:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not speak of this king and priest battle crap, or any other occult nonsense for that matter, in front of me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no interest in what happened in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.65,0:20:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have asked you in the first place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.71,0:20:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's one thing I know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as you have the Millennium Puzzle,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can exist in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Enough{\i0} already!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to be with you forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.96,0:21:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't care if I don't get my memories back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...! I'll always...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you all {\i1}my{\i0} memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The God Card, The Great War God Obelisk, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calling the millions of Anzu fans out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have kept you waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Anzu Masaki, will be performing a Dance Battle at the local game center!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.00,0:21:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll overcome the jerk Step Johnny with my Dance Moves!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.65,0:21:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's settle this with a Duel"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.96,0:21:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Just leave this to me?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, I always knew you were a dependable man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time! "The Fiery Dance Battle"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.00,0:22:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel like I've been here, been in this place before
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With the classroom shaded by the setting sun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I laughed along and pointed with my too shortly cut bangs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.24,0:22:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Little by little, time keeps going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:23:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My bangs now over my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sunset took everyone together
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.92,0:23:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure nothing changed while we were there
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.18,0:23:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I kept on searching for something
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.52,0:23:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you understood such a senseless time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That was the answer
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.41,0:23:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From here, always...
